description:
About

Join us for a chat and presentations relevant to those working, or aspiring to work, in the technology sector.

This event is part of Workshop Wednesdays, hosted by Women's Tech Hub Bristol and you can find the schedule for this day's event here: https://www.meetup.com/Womens-Tech-Hub-Bristol/events/dlmmrrybchbbc/

Women’s Tech Hub runs a no recruiter and a strict social media policy which you can find in their code of conduct.
title: CodeHub @ Workshop Wednesdays
